Util Library of MTK IImageBuffer allocate and metadata convert.

This library is pre-built by MediaTek internal.


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
This contains MediaTek developed camera related pre- and post-processing modules.
Without them, some effecthal module might link error.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:
1.  libstdc++.so
2.  libcutils.so
3.  libutils.so

and the following libs from MediaTek:
1. libcam_utils
2. libcam.metadata

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/libs' folder.

HOW TO USE IT?
==============

Provide api for some camera EffectHal to allocate memory or convert metadata to Exif header. 
all api interface are at (vendor/mediatek/proprietary/hardware/mtkcam)

All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..
